    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/1639" key="#Popes">Urbanus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">episcopus servus servorum</rs> Dei. Dilecto filio *** <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53" key="#Monasteries">Sancti
                            Systi</orgName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/43">Placentini</placeName>, salutem et apostolicam
                        benedictionem. «Ad hoc sumus ad universalis Eclesie regimen Domino
                        disponente assumpti, ut ea que in Eclesia Dei male facta noscuntur per nos
                        ad statum congruum revocentur et bona debeant illibata servari». Sicut autem
                        in audientia nostra est propositum, <persName ref="#people/1615"
                            key="#Abbots">Berardus</persName> quondam abbas <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >cenobii</rs> tui <rs key="#Feudum">infeudavit</rs> plurima de rebus
                        ipsius illiciteque <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">locavit</rs>,
                        sine consensu <rs key="#Churches/religious_bodies">capituli</rs>, propter
                        quod monasterium ipsum magnum detrimentum incurrit. Unde nos, indempnitati
                        eiusdem cenobii paterni sollicitudine providere volentes, infeudationes et
                        locationes possessionum et familiarum <geogName ref="#estates/207"
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Feudum"><placeName
                                ref="#places/462"
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Feudum">Curtis
                                Nove</placeName></geogName> et aliorum locorum ad tuum cenobium
                        pretinencium ab abbate illo contra leges vel canones factas irritas esse
                        censemus, presentis sibi scripti pagina indulgentes ut eas auctoritate
                        nostra libere tibi liceat sine appellationis obstaculo revocare. Datum
                            <placeName ref="#places/59">Verone</placeName> .XVIII. kallendas
                        ianuarii. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
